description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be a game on Steam that has taken the top spot out of quite literally nowhere. This game allows users to click on a picture of a banana and trade over a thousand dollars for a digital banana, why? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: The Biggest Scam On Steam Right Now...
